{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/Logo_EN.gif?t=1738278021\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/Titolo01_EN.png?t=1738278021\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/Titolo02_EN.png?t=1738278021\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">John Doe, a man with no memory, wanders for days through the desert, on the verge of survival. When all seems lost, he spots a remote saloon in the distance: the Bitter Glass. In search of water and shelter, John steps inside\u2026 only to find himself trapped in a place that seems alive and haunted by the souls of the dead. The ghosts inhabiting the saloon are members of the gang, the Demons of the Apocalypse, and they ask John to fulfill their last wishes to finally find peace. But a deeper mystery looms: who is John Doe? And why won\u2019t these souls let him go?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/Titolo03_EN.png?t=1738278021\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Deadly Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_01.png?t=1738278021\" />Uncover the hidden secrets of the Bitter Glass by solving cleverly designed puzzles. Each puzzle serves as a key to better understand John Doe\u2019s past and his connection to the ghosts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mental Health</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_02.png?t=1738278021\" />Every paranormal encounter challenges John\u2019s sanity. Use whiskey to lower his anxiety level, but beware: drinking too much leads to drunkenness, and the only way to sober up is by vomiting. A delicate balance between sanity and clarity is essential to survive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Vengeful Spirits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_03.png?t=1738278021\" />John encounters the members of the &quot;Demons of the Apocalypse,&quot; each with unfinished business. Can he fulfill their requests, or will their thirst for revenge be too strong?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sinister Atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_04.png?t=1738278021\" />From the unsettling shadows of the saloon to the desert dunes, every corner of Lonely Plain hides secrets and dangers that sustain a constant sense of threat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Macabre Music and Sounds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_05.png?t=1738278021\" />The soundtrack and sound effects will fully immerse you in the spectral Wild West of the Bitter Glass, amplifying horror and tension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Revelations and Twists</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_06.png?t=1738278021\" />A mystery that slowly unfolds through terrifying encounters and chilling confessions. Each ghost has a story to tell, and every tale brings John closer to a harrowing truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Letters and Clues</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_07.png?t=1738278021\" />Find and interpret cryptic letters left by those who were trapped here before you. Each message is a piece of the puzzle that helps uncover the secrets of the saloon and its past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Captivating Graphics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_08.png?t=1738278021\" />Detailed environments and realistic lighting make the world of the Bitter Glass both terrifying and immersive, drawing players into a nightmare set in the Wild West.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Constant Tension</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/img_09.png?t=1738278021\" />Every moment is filled with palpable tension, with jumpscares and sudden appearances keeping players on the edge of their seats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3354980/extras/Titolo04.png?t=1738278021\" />Scary Shadow Spot: Bitter Glass is the second chapter of the horror series inspired by The Twilight Zone. With a gripping story and puzzles that will test the mind, this episode takes players on a descent into the inferno of their own past.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A SWEET START","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3354980/7c95e941d177b5744d98f46b6c3c23cfbcd1da0d.jpg"},{"name":"ROOM OF REVELRY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3354980/f88b62c0b97b149c4c95812b4bf13c403b979617.jpg"},{"name":"CANNED MEAT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3354980/a910c2ace5860415